item.title: 4.3 关注项目
item.description: 关注项目 # torvalds/linux # Linux kernel source tree antirez/redis # Redis is an in-memory database that persists on disk. The data model is key-value, but many different kind of values are supported: Strings, Lists, Sets, Sorted Sets, Hashes, Streams, HyperLogLogs, Bitmaps. http://redis.io
